PrecisOrder which exempts the ATLANTIC PILOTAGE AUTHORITY from the requirement to cause an internal audit to be conducted in respect of itself for the next three fiscal years, as provided for in subsection 131(3) of the Financial Administration Act, on the grounds that the benefits to be derived from such audits do not justify their cost.
